    <qandaset id="faq">
      <title>Frequently asked questions</title>
      <qandaentry>
	<question>
	  <para>I get the error: "Couldn't connect to aRts Soundserver. Sound deactivated."</para>
	</question>
	<answer>
	  <para>
               In this release (0.5), KBattleship relies on aRts, KDE's soundserver, to play any sound.
               Enable aRts in kcontrol -> Sound -> Soundserver to solve the problem.
              </para>
	</answer>
      </qandaentry>
      <qandaentry>
	<question>
	  <para>I have a question that is likely to become a FAQ. Who should I contact?</para>
	</question>
	<answer>
	  <para>Contact the authors. They will most likely add it here.</para>
	</answer>
      </qandaentry>
